Package: emergenceModelR
Title: Educational Simulations for Emergence and Complexity
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person(
        given = "Noushin",
        family = "Nabavi",
        role = c("aut", "cre"),
        email = "NoushinN@users.noreply.github.com"
    )
Description: Provides simplified educational simulations for exploring emergence,
    self-organization, complexity, cellular automata, agent interactions, network
    growth, and information-based metrics. The package is intended for teaching,
    science communication, conceptual exploration, and portfolio development. It
    does not claim to model biological life, consciousness, intelligence, or real
    complex systems in full detail.
